\toc1 Jon…®n Ak…®nafarir Namba 3
\mt1 Jon…®n Ak…®nafarir Namba 3
\mt2 O
\mt1 3 Jon
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Sios…®n gumazir dapanir mam ak…®nafarir kam gumazir dapanir igharazim bagha an osiri, an ziam Gaius. A fo, Gaius Krais…®n gumazamizir igharazibar akurvasi, kamagh…®n a Gaius…®n ziam fe. Egha Gaius…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® gumazir kam Diotrefes, a bagh ganigh.
\c 1
\ms1 E God…®n ingangarim gamir gumazamizibar akurvagham
\b
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Aposel 19:29; Rom 16:23; 1 Korin 1:14; 2 Jon 1:1\x*K…® Krais…®n adarazir gumazir dapanim. N…® Gaius, k…® n…® bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri. N…® nan aveghbuamra, ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra bar n…® gifonge.
\v 2 Nan namakar aghuim, k…® n…® bagha God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, n…®n duam derav…®ra iti mogh…®n, n…®n m…®karzim bar derav…®ra ik…®t…®, bizir aghuaribara n…® bativam.
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 2 Jon 1:4\x*N…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n itir marazi iza n…®n gun na m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® derav…®ra guiz…®n akam…®n g…®n zui. Ez…® k…® akar kam baregha bar akonge. K…® fo, n…® zurara guiz…®n akam…®n g…®n zui.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 1 Korin 4:15; Filemon 1:10\x*K…® orazi, nan boriba guiz…®n akam…®n g…®n zuima k…® bar akonge. Nan agoroger kam bizir mabar agorogeba bar dagh afira.
\s1 Gaius ingangarir aghuim gami
\p 
\v 5 Namakar aghuim, n…® zurara derav…®ra guiz…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua egha arazir aghuiba Krais…®n adarazigh ami. Egha n…® fozir puvat…®zir Krais…®n adarasi, n…® uaghan arazir aghuibar me gami.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Taitus 3:13\x*Gumazamizir kaba n…®n arazir gumazamizibagh ifongezim…®n gun kagh itir sios m…®keme. N…® God ifongez…® mogh…®n, n…® bizitaba ua men akuraght…® me da inigh tuavir me zuim…®n mang…®v…®ra ik…®, kamagh…®n dera.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Korin 9:12-15\x*E fo, me Iesus…®n ziam…®n arua ingangarir kam gamuava egha, Krais g…®fozir puvat…®zir gumazamiziba, me men dafaribar biziba isir puvat…®.
\v 8 Ez…® e gumazir kamagh…®n amibar akurvaghs…® bar gavgavigham. E ghaze, e me ko bar mogh…®ra, guiz…®n akam bagh ingars…®, kamagh…®n e men akurvagham.
\s1 Diotrefes arazir kuram gami
\p 
\v 9 K…® sios bagha ak…®nafarir mam osiri. Ez…® Diotrefes uan ziam fa men gumazir dapanim…®n ikiasa, kamagh…®n a nan akam…®n apengan itir puvat…®.
\v 10 Kamagh…®n k…® iz…®va, an arazir kam aghurigham. An en gun tintinibar me m…®g…®a akar kurabar me m…®gei. A kamagh…®ram amir puvat…®, a uaghan Krais…®n adarazi isa uan d…®penim…®n zuir puvat…®. Ez…® igharaz darazi me inigh uan d…®penibar mangasava amima, a uaghan men anogorogha sios…®n aven me batogha, me ab…®si.
\s1 Demitrius arazir aghuim gami
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Onger Akaba 37:27; Aisaia 1:16-17; 1 Pita 3:11; 1 Jon 3:6-10\x*Nan namakar aghuim, n…® arazir kurabar g…®n mangan mark…®, n…® arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®. Gumazamizir arazir aghuibagh amiba, me God…®n boriba. Ez…® gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amiba, me God g…®fozir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Jon 19:35; 21:24\x*Gumazamiziba bar Demitrius…®n arazir aghuim…®n gun m…®gei. Ez…® guiz…®n akam uaghan an arazir aghuim…®n gun m…®gei. Ez…® k…® uaghan an arazir aghuim…®n gun m…®gei. Ez…® ia fo nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba da guizbang…®ra.
\s1 Gumazir dapanim Gaius…®n ganasa
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt 2 Jon 1:12\x*K…® bizir av…®ribar n…® m…®k…®masa, egha k…® da osiran aghua.
\v 14 K…® ghaze, k…® gurumra iz…® n…® batogh ga uaning…®n gan uaning m…®k…®mam.
\v 15 Navir am…®rizim n…® ko ik…®. N…®n namakar kagh itiba akam amaga ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®. Eght…® n…® magh en namakaba vaghvagh kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, Afeziam me ko ik…®.
